      "id": 656,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:3",
      "content": "Implement a \"kill\" button on the S-Deck dashboard that terminates a Claude agent instance (kills its tmux pane) without respawning it.\n\n## What to build\n\n1. **Backend route** in `src/dashboard.ts` — add `POST /api/agents/:agentId/kill`:\n   - Look up the agent (same pattern as the restart handler around line 365)\n   - Validate: agent must exist and have a tmux_pane\n   - Kill the pane: `execSync(`tmux kill-pane -t ${tmux_pane}`)`\n   - Mark the agent ended: `db.prepare('UPDATE agent_status SET ended_at = ? WHERE agent_id = ?').run(Date.now(), agentId)`\n   - Call `reapGhostAgents()` and `purgeStaleAgents()` to clean up\n   - Return `{ ok: true }`\n   - Do NOT respawn — this is a kill, not a restart\n\n2. **Frontend** in `public/index.html` — add a \"kill\" item to the kebab menu on agent cards:\n   - The kebab menu is rendered in `renderAgents()` around line 1269\n   - Only show for non-orchestrator agents (slot > 0), same guard as the restart option\n   - Style it as a destructive action (red text or warning color)\n   - On click, call `fetch('/api/agents/${agentId}/kill', { method: 'POST' })`, then refresh the agent list\n\n## Key files\n- `src/dashboard.ts` — backend routes (restart handler is around line 365, use it as the model)\n- `public/index.html` — frontend (renderAgents function, kebab menu around line 1250-1375)\n- `src/db.ts` — `reapGhostAgents()`, `purgeStaleAgents()`, `getAgentById()` helpers\n\n## Notes\n- No schema changes needed — `ended_at` column already exists\n- The kill route is simpler than restart: kill pane, mark ended, done\n- For the orchestrator (slot 0), do NOT show the kill button\n- After implementing, call `report_done` with a summary of what changed",
      "priority": 5,
      "created_at": 1780681582091,
      "read_at": 1780681585786,
      "needs_approval": 0,
      "approved_at": null,
      "request_options": null,
      "selected_option": null,
      "task_id": null,
      "type": null
    },
    {
      "id": 658,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:3",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "content": "DONE: Kill button implemented.\n\nFiles changed:\n- `src/db.ts`: Added `markAgentEnded(agentId)` helper (exports `UPDATE agent_status SET ended_at`)\n- `src/dashboard.ts`: Imported `markAgentEnded`; added `POST /api/agents/:agentId/kill` route — validates agent exists + has tmux pane + is not slot 0 + not already ended, kills pane, marks ended, reaps/purges\n- `public/index.html`: Added `kill-item` button to kebab menu (non-orchestrator only, red text via `color:var(--error)`), wired click handler with confirm dialog that POSTs to `/api/agents/:id/kill` then lets SSE refresh the list\n\nBuild: `tsc` passes clean, no errors.",
